                    "title": "Safety equipment welding",
                    "description": "",
                    "comment": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Watch the clip: <strong><em>10 safety clips welding</em></strong>. <span class=\"font-size-14px\">The narrator gives ten items that help protect you when welding. He also states why and how. Fill in the scheme. If necessary stop the clip. Advice: watch it several times.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"underline\"><em><strong>Item</strong></em></span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p><strong><em>Description material</em></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p><em><strong>Specifics</strong></em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li>Safety Jacket</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p>Cow leather</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li>Gloves</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<ol>\n<li> </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-201-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/1/16ef7e630656810ca65875cee46dd09c80219921.jpg\" class=\"height-265-pixels width-190-pixels float-right\"/></p>\n"
