                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><strong><span class=\"underline\">Assignment: Meaningful sentences</span></strong></p>\n<p>Go to the vocabulary list of Beroepsspecifiek Engels Mechatronica. Choose 10 words and use them making 5 sentences in which is clear what the meaning of these words are.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<p>Words: <em>employer</em> and <em>electrical power.</em></p>\n<p>Sentence: The employer complained about the amount of electrical power being used by his employees.</p>\n<p>1.    <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/8/868e57b70dab4201fd49b6edcc437016b6d8cde7.jpg\" class=\"height-194-pixels width-259-pixels float-right\"/>    </p>\n<p>2.        </p>\n<p>3.        </p>\n<p>4.        </p>\n<p>5.        </p>\n"
